This is Conway's Game of Life implementation for Android Honeycomb.

FEATURES
========
* Gameloop with pausing and option to fix framerate
* Draws the board using bitmaps (png)
* Editing of the board, using touch.
* Panning and zooming the board, using pinch to zoom.
* Configure game using settings, including choosing different theme.
* Uses the action bar.

DEPENDENCIES
============
Android 3.2 at the moment.


INSTALLATION
============
Choose Downloads, download the application 'GameOfLife.apk'. Sideload it to your
honeycomb tablet. Install it.

HACKING
=======
See the file HACKING in the root folder of the project.
